# Follow the Leader (Snap Program)

This is an interactive animation created in **Snap!** at UC Berkeley.

### Play it here  
https://snap.berkeley.edu/embed?projectname=Follow%20the%20leader&username=abigail%20d%2e&showTitle=true&showAuthor=true&editButton=true&pauseButton=true

### Description
When Peterpan says "Go," move your cursor in front of him!  
He will follow your cursor and learn to fly.  
